				</div>
				<div class="flex-initial max-w-50 px-2 heading-text-heading" style="font-size: 20px;
				line-height: 2.0;
				font-weight: 200;">
					<h1>Who are We</h1>
					<p>Uncle Buck’s is a non-profit organization that was Birthed out of the loss of a wonderful father, pastor, and friend.
						 <!-- Uncle Buck’s provides restoration to young men across the greater Atlanta area.  -->
						 <!-- Our founder noticed that there was a need for more than just the latest pair of sneakers for young men in the spiritual, professional, and educational realms.  -->
						 After the loss of his father, Rev. Curlee “Uncle Buck” Windham, Sr., Todd Windham turned their bonding time into a service for young men, restoring quality shoes for quality men. 
					</p>
				</div>
				
			</div>
		</div>
